        <article>
            <h2>haven</h2>

            <dl>
                <dt>Project type:</dt>
                <dd>Public mobile app, website</dd>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>

                <dt>Plaform:</dt>
                <dd>iOS and Android</dd>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>

                <dt>Stack:</dt>
                <dd>AngularJS on Cordova, NodeJS and MongoDB on Heroku</dd>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>

                <dt>Contributions:</dt>
                <dd>Interaction design, UI design, full stack development as part of a team of 4 full-time developers. Also performed user testing and conducted user-interviews to improve prouct design and fit.</dd>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>

                <dt>Challenge:</dt>
                <dd>Develop a product for a unproven market of digital management of home services and the tools for homeowners to take better care of their homes.</dd>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>

            </dl>

            <h3>Summary:</h3>
            <p>Haven provided services to homeowners that helped them to both understand what they need to do to maintain their home as well as making it easy to hire professionals. Initially, consumers used Haven via an installed mobile app, but was later expanded to incorporate a responsive web app and even phone and SMS service. Order tracking was managed using custom, web-based admin tools, Trello and on-staff customer service.</p>
        </article>

    </section>

